            <tr>
              <td><p class="style7 txt style8"><b>Welcome and thank you for visiting our site.</b></p>
                <p class="style7 txt"><b>History<br>
                </b>Northwood <strong>Food Machinery</strong> is an established family run business.
                  The company was founded in 1989 and originally manufactured
                  equipment for the bakery industry. Since our early beginnings
                  we have grown to encompass conveyor systems and <strong>cheese cutting
                  machinery</strong> into our expanding portfolio.</p>
                <p class="style7 txt"><b>Why choose Northwood?<br>
                </b>Our staff have many years experience in the food industry
                  and understand your processes. We have the knowledge to integrate
                  sound engineering concepts into modern day food production
                  environments.</p>
                <p class="txt style7">We pride ourselves on the high standard
                    of our work and strive to produce quality equipment that
                    is built to last. Since all our projects are designed and
                    managed “in-house” we are able
                  to offer flexible solutions to meet your requirements whilst
                  remaining extremely competitive. </p>
                <p class="txt style7">If you are looking for a friendly, professional approach then
                  we are here to help.</p>
                <p class="style7 txt"><b>A problem to solve ?<br>
                </b>Over the years
                  we have designed so many “one off” machines
                  that it would be impractical to list them all. If the equipment
                  listed on this site does not cover your application then we
                  may well be able to offer a bespoke solution. </p>
                <p class="txt style7">Please contact us to discuss your automation requirements. <a href="mailto:mike.nfm@googlemail.com" >mike.nfm@googlemail.com</a></p>
				
        <p class="txt style7" align="center"><a href="javascript:ShowContent('moreinfo')">[+] More Information</a> <a href="javascript:HideContent('moreinfo')">[-] Close</a></p>
        <div id="moreinfo" style="position:relative;display:none;">
          <h3 class="txt style7"><strong>Bakery Industry Equipment</strong></h3><p class="txt style7">Northwood have been manufacturing sausage roll machines and pasty machines plus associated equipment such as flour dusters, depositors and travelling guillotines for two decades. Our expertise extends to pastry plant, pastry sheeters, cake cutting machines and now pie machines.</p>
           <h3 class="txt style7"><strong>Conveyors</strong></h3><p class="txt style7">Every belt conveyor, modular belt conveyor, slat band conveyor, retracting conveyor and wire belt conveyor is manufactured in stainless steel and other food quality materials. Northwood manufacture conveyors that are built to endure the rigours of the food industry with hygiene a key consideration in all our designs.</p>
           <h3 class="txt style7"><strong>Dairy Industry Equipment</strong></h3><p class="txt style7">Our reputation for building high quality cheese cutting machines is underlined by business from some of the biggest names in the dairy industry. We now build cheese cutters for Cheddar, Emmental, Stilton, Edam, Mozzarella, Feta, Havarti and Halloumi Cheese. 
		  </p>
      </div></p>
